{"id":232953619,"title":"首爾光化門廣場 (광화문광장)","content":"光化門廣場(광화문광장)就位於景福宮前方，光化門曾做為景福宮正門，歷經多次毀壞和遷移，2006年韓國政府開始重建光化門，歷經3年9個月的施工，於2010年8月15日韓國光復節重新對外開放。\n\n如同臺北的凱達格蘭大道，光化門廣場為首爾最具指標的群眾陳抗地點，不僅離青瓦台和韓國行政機關近，美國駐韓大使館也在旁邊，讓光化門廣場格外受到矚目。\n\n廣場上現有世宗大王(세종대왕)和李舜臣(이순신)將軍銅像各一座，世宗大王為朝鮮史上最有為的君主，李舜臣則是朝鮮時期壬辰倭亂對抗日本的名將，至今仍是韓國人的民族英雄。\n\n若是搭乘地鐵可坐到5號線的光化門站，地鐵出口即是光化門廣場，或是坐到3號線的景福宮站亦可，從景福宮站走過來也不遠。來景福宮參觀的朋友，不妨順道到前面的光化門廣場走走。\n\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/kXFMPzT.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/ZMrONU0.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/qy8X59X.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/vmRS5PN.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/QxZBYfl.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/Qn3gIsN.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/DQVlcga.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/GQzXcsR.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/qek1dYV.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/P30Lkaz.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/GSejfGv.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/Zbd5KZt.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/4JTNmEL.jpg\n更多照片和介紹: https://peavy.pixnet.net/blog/post/48871386","excerpt":"光化門廣場（광화문광장）就位於景福宮前方，光化門曾做為景福宮正門，歷經多次毀壞和遷移，2006年韓國政府開始重建光化門，歷經3年9個月的施工，於2010年8月15日韓國光復節重新對外開放。如同臺北的凱","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"a255fb97-4199-4bd0-9b28-1ec2c0d2f382","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-25T03:16:34.383Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T03:16:34.383Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":6,"tags":[],"topics":["首爾","自由行","遊記","旅遊","韓國"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"旅遊","forumAlias":"travel","school":"Xavier","department":"sanchers","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":6}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/kXFMPzT.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/ZMrONU0.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/qy8X59X.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/vmRS5PN.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/QxZBYfl.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/Qn3gIsN.jpg"},{"url